X of type block.
Y of type block.
H of type h.
W of type place.

executable pick(X,Y,H,W) if top(X,W), on(X,Y), height(W,H), free_gripper.

executable pick_from_barrier(X) if barrier(X), free_gripper.

executable put(X,Y,H,W) if gripped(X), top(Y,W), height(W,H-1), neg free_gripper.

executable put_on_barrier(X) if gripped(X), free_barrier, neg free_gripper.



pick(X,Y,H,W) causes gripped(X), neg height(W, H), height(W, H-1), neg free_gripper, neg top(X,W).
pick(X,Y,H,W) causes top(Y,W), neg on(X,Y) if on(X,Y).
pick_from_barrier(X) causes gripped(X), neg free_gripper, free_barrier, barrier(X).

put(X,Y,H,W) causes neg top(Y,W), on(X,Y) if top (Y,W).
put(X,Y,H,W) causes top(X,W), neg height(W,H-1), height(W,H), free_gripper, neg gripped(X).
put_on_barrier(X) causes free_gripper, neg gripped(X), neg free_barrier, barrier(X).